Tuɣalem d axxam yebnan ɣef leḥrir, leɛbada akk-d Izimer n Ṛebbi. Imeslayen-agi ț-țbibbin n ddheb, d lkețțan azeggaɣ ɣlayen n mkul ṣṣenf akk-d ddheb,
Awal-agi d awal n tideț yuklalen ad ițwaqbel s lekmal-is : « Wagi d ameqqran ».
kečč s yiman-ik ilaq aț-țiliḍ d lemtel s lecɣal-ik yelhan, sselmad seg wul akk-d țideț,
Skud mazal nezmer a nekcem ɣer westeɛfu i ɣ-yewɛed Sidi Ṛebbi, ilaq a nbecceṛ daɣen deg unezṛuf ; yeɛni ayen i d-iqqaṛ ayen ur nesɛi azal, yemxalafen a yemxalafen.
S tideț, llan kra țbecciṛen Lmasiḥ s ṭṭmeɛ akk-d zzux ; meɛna wiyaḍ țbecciṛen s wul yeṣfan d neyya.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen meṛṛa.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di lǧețța-s yerna yessamas akk taṛwiḥt-nneɣ,
Ssutren-ik a d-yedṛu yid-ek yiwet n taddart isem-is : sseǧhed-ik a k-id-yawi ɣer webrid, s timsalin-agi ara d-yawin timeslayin ur nețwassen ara, wayeḍ a tent-id isbeggen s imeslayen-agi, s wakka i d-yekkan si wayen i d-iqqaṛ !
Nenna-yawen-t-id : ma yella tesneḍlem-ik here, tețțusemmaḍ di tesselmadeḍ i wiyaḍ, eɛni ur k-tufi ara, tzemreḍ aț-țessiweḍ lexbaṛ i tutlayin ur nețwassen ara ?
iwakken a d-qiṛṛen s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, aț-țɛeqleḍ belli d at Isṛail i d-yusan si tmurt n Sban, a ten-immeslayen. D annect-agi i k-d-issawlen, yewwi-d lḥal armi i t-id-slemdeɣ.
Axaṭer ussan-nni d ussan n twaɣit deg wacu ara yedṛu wannect-agi, ass n tuɣalin n ccariɛa akk-d tbeddleḍ, ulac ayen ara ččen.
Aɛeqqa-yagi d nețța i d amecṭuḥ meṛṛa ger zzerriɛat yellan, lameɛna mi gețwazreɛ, igemmu yețțali alamma yekka-d sennig akk yemɣan n tebḥirt, yeggar-ed ifurkawen d imeqqranen, ula d ifṛax n igenni , bennun leɛcuc-nsen s ufella-s.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Yețwali deg wayen i d-qqaṛeɣ Sidna Ɛisa : ț-țagi i d yețmeslayen seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit weṛǧin di tmurt n Yahuda.
Akken qṛib ad yaweḍ Sidna Ɛisa ɣer temdint n Yiriku, yiwen uɛeqqa n yired yeɣlin deg uxerḍel.
Di lweqt-nni, yiwen umeḥbus mechuṛen tabṛaḥt n temdint n Biririn yusa-d, mačči d wid yellan di tmurt n Selyan i gellan di leswaṛ n temdint n Babilun.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen seg uḥeccad, tețțuleqmeḍ ɣef tzemmurt n lɛali ɣas akken d aḥeccad i telliḍ, acḥal ihi i sen-ishel i nutni yellan ț-țiṣeḍwa n tzemmurt iwakken ad uɣalen ad țțuleqmen ɣef tzemmurt-iw.
Tella dinna yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu, tețfeǧǧiǧ di mkul amkan ; ma d kečč s yiman-ik tewtem-t.
Meɛna ma yella nekk yewwi-d lḥal ad iwɛiɣ imukan imezwura di tmeɣṛiwin, ad țwaɛeddan alamma d ass wis xemsin. Twaɣit-agi, aț-țiliḍ s yiwet n tama tayeffust neɣ taɛeṣṣabt n yiṭij meɛna tesraft.
Deg ifragen-agi aṭas n imuḍan i gḍelqen, iderɣalen, iɛibanen d wukrifen țṛaǧun akk ad ḥerrken waman.
Walit acḥal meqqeṛ leḥmala n Sidna Ɛisa, acḥal ɣezzif di lmedwed, acḥal i geɣlil ɣer tmenṭac n lexla, armi ț-țamurt n tmurt n Yahuda leɛmeṛ !
A d-tbanent licaṛat deg iṭij, ilaq a kkun-nhuɣ aț-țettixṛem i neyya d ṣṣfa n wul-nsen.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid. ?effus n leḥyuḍ n yemdanen yid-es ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ,
seg yiwet n tama reggmen-kkun, kksen fell-awen sser, si tama nniḍen tbeddem.
Lɛid i deg xeddmen wat Isṛail tiɛecciwin iqeṛṛeb-ed.
wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ ad frun tilufa-nsen mi llan di tmurt n Yahuda akk-d Lmasiḥ i d-yusan si tmurt n ddunit, ad amnen s waṭas n lɛaddat n yemdanen ;
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni deg wayen n wass n lɛid n Tfaska, bɣan ad kksen di leɛwaǧeb-nni deg umenɣi.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed lmuqeddem n Lmasiḥ seg wesfel kan, mačči s ɣuṛ-sen i d-yekka ; lameɛna sɛan kra n tukciwin i d-yusan si tmurt n Yahuda akk-d wid n wat Isṛail, wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass n Tfaska n izimer n leslak i deg xeddmen kra n lɛaddat nniḍen : ț-țameddit n wass n westeɛfu, qṛib a d-yaweḍ wass n lɛid n Tfaska, wid i d-yusan ad stenfeɛ lɣaci, iwakken ad țțuẓummen lecyux n wat Isṛail iwakken ad țțuẓummen wat Isṛail.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, a ț-issers ɣef yixef n lexla, bɣan a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid neɣ a t-stiḥeq.
Imi nuggad a ɣ-yawi waḍu ɣer leryuf iweɛṛen n tmurt n Libya, ncudd lbabuṛ s imurar ; nerna nṣubb-ed lbac-nni s wayes i t-yețțawi waḍu, neǧǧa iman-nneɣ a ɣ-yawi ɣer wanda yebɣa.
Lameɛna imi d lexdayem n ddunit meṛṛa, tagellit n tmurt n Galasya : n lebḥuṛ akk-d wid yețwaḍebɛen ( imekkasen ) lewqam, i yeqjan, izuɣaṛen n lexla akk-d wezṛu yellan d iselman ( lḥut ) n tmurt n Jlili.
M'ara d-taseḍ, amenzu ara d-yezɣuṛen seg umalu, neɣ agummaḍ i lebḥeṛ neɣ ț-țigzirt, zwiǧen-as tmes deg uqeṛṛu-nni, imiren ma llan ț-țaggara n ddunit a ten-id-yaweḍ.
Sufella n usenduq-agi rsent snat n lmeṣnuɛat imetlen lmalayekkat, ɣumment s tili n wafriwen-nsent amkan-nni i țṛuccun s idammen n iseflawen i leɛfu n ddnubat.
Imi aṭas n lɣaci i gețṛuḥun țțuɣalen-d, ur sɛin ara lweqt ad slen i wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi ; ilaq ad ččen azeggaɣ, yerna ad țeklen ayen s wayes ara kemmlen abrid-nsen.
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen. Refden amextaf n lbabuṛ, ṛuḥen rrif rrif n tegzirt n Kritus.
Teččam lḥeqq n wid imegren igran-nsen, slet-asen i wigi ițcetkin ɣef lbaṭel-nsen neɣ ɣef lbaṭel-nsen.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen imednuben, iwakken ad sɛun amkan anda ur neǧhid ara di liman, ur kkatet ara deg-s d acu i s-ițwakkes.
Ma d nutni ilaq a ten-sbedden wid yextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, d wid i gxeddmen ccɣel-nsen, yerna ilaq a t-nhuɣ iwakken ur t-țxeddem ara.
